data.description: Step Into Elegance With A Two-Story Foyer And Living Room. This Home Boasts A Separate Dining Room, An Open-Concept Layout, And A Kitchen With Stainless Steel Appliances. The Patio Door Opens To A Deck, Creating A Seamless Connection To The Outdoors, While The Family Room Features A Cozy Fireplace For Warmth And Comfort. Ascend To The Second Floor, Where You'll Discover Three Bedrooms Sharing A Hall Bath. The Main Bedroom Has A Vaulted Ceiling, A Private Ensuite Featuring A Double Vanity, And A Generously Sized Walk-In Closet, Ensuring Comfort And Convenience. The Basement Presents A Semi-Finished Space Complemented By A Partially Completed Bathroom. Step Outside To A Generously Fenced Backyard, Indulge In Hot Summer Nights, And Refreshingly Swim In The Above-Ground Pool. The Home Also Features A Spacious 3.5-Car Tandem Garage, Ample Parking, And Storage-Newer HVAC, A/C, Microwave And Dishwasher. The Property Is Located Near I-80, I-55, Rt. 52, IL 59 And Joliet Junior College. A Must See!
